<p>Inside: Inside the shop she stood near a table display </p>

<p>She promoted her appearance at the store on Instagram, sharing a photo standing in front of a red shoe table display.  </p>

<p>Sarah used shoe boxes to prop up a Macbook lap top with a ring light standing behind it. </p>

<p>'Dateline New York City,' she captioned the photo. '54th between 5th and 6th. I'm here until my parent/teacher conference.'</p>

<p>Co-workers: She mingled with the workers of the shop and customers </p>

